'''克卜勒62f'''<ref name="Borucki" /><ref name="NASA-20130418" /><ref name="NYT-20130418">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |title=2 Good Places to Live, 1,200 Light-Years Away |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/19/science/space/2-new-planets-are-most-earth-like-yet-scientists-say.html |date=18 April 2013 |publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=18 April 18 |archive-date=2017-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225034011/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/19/science/space/2-new-planets-are-most-earth-like-yet-scientists-say.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang en|'''Kepler-62f'''}}），亦稱'''KOI-701.04'''，是一顆環繞[[天琴座|天琴座]]恆星[[克卜勒62|克卜勒62]]的[[太陽系外行星|系外]][[超級地球|超級地球]]，是已知距離母恆星最遠的行星，由[[NASA|NASA]]的[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]以偵測行星通過恆星前方造成亮度下降的凌日法發現。<ref>[http://arxiv.org/abs/1304.5058 Water Planets in the Habitable Zone: Atmospheric Chemistry, Observable Features, and the case of Kepler-62e and -62f] {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1304.5058 |date=20140816155954 }}, L. Kaltenegger, D. Sasselov, S. Rugheimer, 18 Apr 2013</ref>它很可能是一顆位於[[適居帶|適居帶]]中的[[類地行星|類地行星]]<ref name = "Borucki">{{Cite journal | last=Borucki | first=William J. | authorlink=威廉·博魯奇 | coauthors=''et al.'' | title=Kepler-62: A Five-Planet System with Planets of 1.4 and 1.6 Earth Radii in the Habitable Zone | journal=Science Express | date=18 April 2013 | url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/early/2013/04/17/science.1234702 | doi=10.1126/science.1234702 | accessdate=18 April 2013 | archive-date=2013-05-03 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20130503100306/http://www.sciencemag.org/content/early/2013/04/17/science.1234702 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="spacecomkepler62f">{{Cite web |url=http://www.space.com/24142-kepler-62f.html |title=Kepler-62f: A Possible Water World |accessdate=2014-01-05 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613184156/https://www.space.com/24142-kepler-62f.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="space.com kepler">{{Cite web |url=http:/