== 文化影響 ==
於2013年5月9日，一個由兩位[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]小組委員會因天文學家們發現了克卜勒62f，而舉辦的國會聽證會討論了「太陽系外行星的發現：我們是否有其他的地球？」（{{lang|en|Exoplanet Discoveries: Have We Found Other Earths?}}）這個議題。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://science.house.gov/hearing/subcommittee-space-and-subcommittee-research-joint-hearing-exoplanet-discoveries-have-we |title=Subcommittee on Space and Subcommittee on Research Joint Hearing - Exoplanet Discoveries: Have We Found Other Earths? |accessdate=2013-12-11 |archive-date=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207205111/https://science.house.gov/hearing/subcommittee-space-and-subcommittee-research-joint-hearing-exoplanet-discoveries-have-we |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[科學_(期刊)|科學]]》亦同時出版了一個關於發現系外行星的專刊。<ref name="SCI-20130503">{{cite journal |authors=Staff |title=Special Issue: Exoplanets |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/site/special/exoplanets/ |date=May 3, 2013 |journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] |accessdate=May 18, 2013 |archive-date=2019-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803082016/https://www.sciencemag.org/site/special/exoplanets/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[搜寻地外文明计划|搜寻地外文明计划]]也將克卜勒62f和其他克卜勒62行星列為候選外星生命家園之一。<ref name="Kepler-62 SETI">{{cite web |title=Has Kepler Found Ideal SETI-target Planets? |url=http://www.seti.org/seti_kepler_62 |date=19 April 2013 |work=[[SETI_Institute|SETI Institute]] |accessdate=17 September 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029212645/http://www.seti.org/seti_kepler_62 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

